                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>Office of the Jewish Messenger</placeName>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>119 West Houston Street</placeName>.</p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>May 10th 1864</date>.</p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Esteemed Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">The Bible &amp; prayer<lb/> books reached us yesterday<lb/> in good\n                order.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">As regards the<lb/>\n                <add>Hebrew</add> you inquired about, the<lb/> prices are $12 and $25.— to<lb/> you,\n                $10 and $22. Are these<lb/> rates conformable to your expecta<lb/>tions? If so, let\n                us know<lb/> &amp; the number you order will<lb/> be promptly forwarded.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">We sympathize in<lb/> your recital concerning advanced<lb/> rates of\n                labor. There appears to<lb/> be no help for it. We can only submit.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33x8460m/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
