                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"indent(1)\">My father desires me to<lb/> say that he knows nothing<lb/> whatever\n                of the matter you<lb/> refer to, concerning the inquiry<lb/> put to him by\n                    <persName>Mr Solis</persName>. He<lb/> is entirely ignorant of the affair<lb/>\n                and has not been applied to by<lb/> anybody with reference to it. He<lb/> says that\n                he “thought you knew<lb/> him better than to put such<lb/> a question.”</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">With respect to the Board of<lb/> Delegates, I can inform you<lb/>\n                of one accession—that of the<lb/>\n                <placeName>Clinton St.</placeName> congregation of this city.<lb/> I am trying to\n                bring the others<lb/> in, but the <persName>Wise</persName>-Germanic influence<lb/>\n                is too strong. If you have drafted<lb/> any document you would like to<lb/> have\n                issued, you might send it<lb/> to me as soon as you please<lb/> There will be a\n                meeting of the</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p33x8460m/canvas/p2"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
